
units           metal
boundary        p p p
atom_style      atomic
newton          on
lattice         fcc 3.61
region          box block 0 1 0 1 0 1
create_box      1 box
create_atoms    1 box
pair_style      tensormd
pair_coeff      * * CuHe_m3k64_M_silu_fp64.npz Cu timer on
neighbor        1.0 bin
neigh_modify	delay 0 every 1 check yes
fix             1 all nve
thermo          1
thermo_style    custom step etotal vol pxx pyy pzz
timestep        0.001
run             1

